                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
                        <!--  *************************************  <handDesc>  ********************************* -->
                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote ana="#impressed.inscribed">
                                <p>Square script with the exception of a few rounded characters. The
                                    letters are deeply and carefully cut , but lack a straight
                                    alignment</p>
                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>
                        <!--  *************************************  <decoDesc>  ********************************* -->
                        <decoDesc>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Depicted cross-chi symbol in the form of a helix</ab>
                                <locus>Inside the upper right corner of the frame</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Deeply incised frame, partially preserved at its lower part</ab>
                                <locus>Encloses the epitaph and its symbolic decoration</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Outlined cross with a chi sign in its center and a bird facing
                                    it</ab>
                                <locus>Incised at the end of the epitaph</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Incised cross forming a central lozenge and small triangles as
                                    bars </ab>
                                <locus>Below the inscription, almost in the middle</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Schematically carved bird</ab>
                                <locus>Below the inscription, to the left of the cross</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                            <decoNote>
                                <ab>Plain cross with linear serifs</ab>
                                <locus>Incised below the bird</locus>
                            </decoNote>
                        </decoDesc>
